      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……ナイトプールに大勢呼んで撮影しようだなんて\nkanaとは、とことん感性が合わないわね……",
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.4200000048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "前は貸し切りだったし、優雅で良かったのに。しかも\nkanaの友達がエキストラとか、居心地悪過ぎますよ",
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき早めに来ていた方々と、控室で話して\nましたよね？　和やかな雰囲気に見えましたけど",
      "startTime": 23.7425335033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "あれは仕事の一環です\n笑顔を振りまくのが最低限のマナーですよ",
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "というか、kanaの交友関係って\n一体どうなってるんですか？　節操なさ過ぎますよ",
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "インフルエンサーの子達と延々と一緒に写真を\n撮らされたと思ったら",
      "startTime": 42.4531357286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "今度は大企業のかっちりした大人に\nご丁寧に名刺を渡されたりして……",
      "startTime": 45.8025628488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "温度差も凄くて、気疲れしたんですけど……\nこの後、もっと増えるんですよね……",
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、顔が広いですからね\n俺もここまでいろんな人が来るとは思いませんでした",
      "startTime": 57.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "しかもみんなして律儀に挨拶に来るから\n余計にしんどいんですよね……",
      "startTime": 63.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～。早く帰ってサバイバル漫画の新刊が読みたい\n今すっごい面白いとこなのに……",
      "startTime": 70.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "撮影前からそんな悲しいことを言わないで下さい\nとりあえず、撮影の準備をしましょうか",
      "startTime": 77,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ。なんで私達、こんな雑用をやらされてる訳？",
      "startTime": 81.6666687567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "人手が足りないからしょうがないですよ",
      "startTime": 86.6666687567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "だからって、機材の設営とかケーブルの配線とかまで\nやらされるのはおかしいでしょ！？",
      "startTime": 93.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "kanaのやつ、私をあごで使って！　しかも\nネチネチと細かいことにケチつけてくるんですよ！？",
      "startTime": 99,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "姑か、って文句を言ってやったら「山田さんライトの\n隅に埃が残ってましてよ」とか余計に言ってくるし",
      "startTime": 105.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "ほんっっっとうに屈辱だわ！　史上最悪の監督よ！\nって……ああもう、また呼ばれるし。なんなのよ……",
      "startTime": 115.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.9979099,
          "startTime": 120.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "startTime": 122.8592087029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "照明の位置的に、もう少しこっちから撮った方が\n衣装が映えていいかもしれないですね",
      "startTime": 129.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "そう……そんな感じです。ありがとうございます\nえぇ、これでもっと見栄えが良くなると思います！",
      "startTime": 135.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、みなさん\nここは意外と段差があるので気を付けて下さいね",
      "startTime": 140.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "意外と冷えますから、この毛布を使って下さい\n温かい飲み物はここにあるので、いつでも飲んで下さい",
      "startTime": 148.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 1499.996383999985,
          "startTime": 146.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（franさん、不満はあるみたいだけど……）\n（エキストラを入れたシーンからは、切り替えてるな）",
      "startTime": 155.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、てきぱき働きながら\n周りにも絶えず気を配って、凄いですね",
      "startTime": 160.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "本当は嫌ですよ。もっと撮影に集中したいですから\nでも……人手が足りないんですよね",
      "startTime": 169.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "これで円滑に進むなら、やるしかないじゃないですか\nいい作品を作るためなら、妥協は出来ないので",
      "startTime": 176.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんもちゃちゃっと動いて下さい\nなるべくスムーズにこの撮影を終わらせて……ん？",
      "startTime": 182.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
